Package: dlexDB
Title: Interface to the dlexDB Lexical Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Reinhold", "Kliegl", email = "reinhold.kliegl@uni-potsdam.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an interface to the dlexDB corpus based on the DWDS core corpus. 
    It automatically downloads, caches, and queries lexical statistics using DuckDB and Parquet files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
